gobblin.data.management.conversion.hive.source

Class HiveWorkUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.configuration.State
      • gobblin.source.workunit.WorkUnit
        • gobblin.data.management.conversion.hive.source.HiveWorkUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WritableShim

    public class HiveWorkUnit
extends WorkUnit
    A WorkUnit wrapper for HiveSource. This is class is meant to hide the keys at which workunit values are stored. The source class is supposed to read/write values into the WorkUnit through getters/setters instead of directly accessing through State.getProp(String, String)/State.setProp(String, Object)
